{"tid":26733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【爆煲風波】樂視A股開市忽然停牌！ 有重大事項公佈","createTime":"2016-12-07T01:43:40.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T09:11:21.000Z","uid":39464,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d918d06115d4e1465a358a945b16e79d982c6faf","tid":26733,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T01:43:40.000Z","msg":"昨日傳出樂視將裁員20%，又指樂視體育總編輯敖銘已辭職，謠言滿天，樂視A股於今早開市前忽然停牌，指將公佈重大事項，臨時停牌。<br />\n<br />\n樂視昨日受裁員消息困擾，A股昨日跌近8%，收報35.8元人民幣。樂視為大股東的酷派（2369〕昨日下跌近5%，今早開市前跌1.25%，開報0.79元。<br />\n<br />\n內地傳媒《懶熊體育》引述消息稱，樂視體育內部已决定整體裁員，幅度將達到20%，其中智能硬件部門的裁員幅度高達50%；於今年5月11日先加盟的樂視體育總編輯敖銘，據悉已遞交信辭職，至離職日只上任短短7個月。其後內地新浪引述樂視回應稱，「樂視體育整體的優化幅度在10%左右，不同部門不盡相同，具體優化比例根據各業務經營實際情況而定。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56014133&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161207\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56014133%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161207&d=1PqeU65tlB6pUrEWQ1zVbWN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=c1af4f61\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56014133%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161207&h=cce8286f\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56014133&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161207</a>"},{"pid":"ee407b8c17b7d49e2a87e9efe1fd5b8b8c135ac2","tid":26733,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T01:46:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8afaa57037f073c2858a93ffbac2f15f1df6ba9d","tid":26733,"uid":36544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T01:47:55.000Z","msg":"樂爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"